'''三苯基六氟磷酸碳'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为{{chem|C|19|H|15|F|6|P}}，或写成{{chem|(C|6|H|5|)|3|C|PF|6}}，由{{le|三苯甲基正离子|Triphenylcarbenium}}（{{chem|[(C|6|H|5|)|3|C]|+}}）和[[六氟磷酸盐|六氟磷酸根]]阴离子（{{chem|[PF|6|]|-}}）构成。它是棕色粉末，可以迅速水解为[[三苯甲醇|三苯甲醇]]。它是有机合成中的[[催化剂|催化剂]]和反应试剂。<ref name=Urch>{{cite journal |author=Urch, C. |title=Triphenylmethyl Hexafluorophosphate |journal=Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis |year=2001 |doi=10.1002/047084289X.rt363f|isbn=0471936235 }}</ref>

==制备==
三苯基六氟磷酸碳可由[[六氟磷酸银|六氟磷酸银]]和[[三苯氯甲烷|三苯基氯甲烷]]反应得到：<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Sharp, D. |author2=Shepard, N. |title=Complex Fluorides. Part VIII |journal=University Chemical Laboratory, Cambridge |year=1956 |pages=674–682}}</ref>

:AgPF<sub>6</sub> + (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>3</sub>CCl → (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>3</sub>CPF<sub>6</sub> + AgCl

另一种方法则利用了三苯甲醇的质子交换反应：<ref name=Olah>{{cite journal |title=Preparative Carbocation Chemistry; IV. Improved Preparation of Triphenylcarbenium (Trityl) Salts |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_synthesis_1972-10_10/page/544 |journal=Synthesis |volume=1972 |issue=10 |pages=544 |year=1972 |author1=Olah, G. |author2=Svoboda, J. |author3=Olah, J. |doi= 10.1055/s-1972-21914}}</ref>

:HPF<sub>6</sub> + (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>3</sub>COH → (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>3</sub>CPF<sub>6</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>O

